Marilyn Erskine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marilyn_Erskine 0 Marilyn Erskine (born April 24, 1926) is an American actress who started performing at the age of three on radio, and has since appeared in radio, theater, film and television roles from the 1920s through the 1970s.
